column2: SELECT TOP #   m.OBJID AS akari_ID,   m.RA AS akari_ra,   m.DEC AS akari_dec,   o.z AS redshift,   o.zErr AS err_redshift,   o.class,   o.modelMag_u AS u,   o.modelMag_g AS g,   o.modelMag_r AS r,   o.modelMag_i AS i,   o.modelMag_z AS z,   o.modelMagErr_u AS uErr,   o.modelMagErr_g AS gErr,   o.modelMagErr_r AS rErr,   o.modelMagErr_i AS iErr,   o.modelMagErr_z AS zErr,      n.objid, n.distance into mydb.output2        from MyDB.akari_subset AS m     CROSS APPLY fGetNearestObjEq( m.RA, m.DEC, #) AS n     INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS o ON n.objid = o.specObjID
